                        <span>**Regeneration**: Cutting the Vagus Nerve in a healthy mammal should result in regrowth, similar to how a Nemertean proboscis regenerates.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-vagus-blue rounded-full mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
